<div class="landing py-5 my-5">
  <section id="home_hero" class="hero text-center pb-5">
    <h1 class="display-1 fw-800 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.05;">
      <span class="d-block">Mettez en avant</span>
      <span class="d-block pb-3 background-gradient">votre collection Magic.</span>
    </h1>
    <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
      <p class="fs-4 mt-5" style="line-height: 1.25;">
        <span class="d-block">Recherchons ensemble toutes tes cartes une par une.</span>
        <span class="d-block pb-2">Et évaluons le prix de ta collection !</span>
      </p>
      <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-center align-items-center mt-4">
        <%= link_to "Recherche tes cartes →", search_cards_path, class: "btn btn-dark btn-lg" %>
        <%= link_to "Evalue ta collection", cards_path, class: "btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg ms-0 ms-md-2 mt-2 mt-md-0" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

<div class="container marketing">
  <div class="flex-center flex-column py-4 mb-3">
    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2
          class="featurette-heading col-12 col-md-5 d-flex flex-column mb-3 order-md-2">Cet outil va te permettre de
          <span class="text-muted">trouver tes cartes.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="lead">Tu vas trouver toutes tes cartes de façon rapide et simple à la fois !<br>Soit patient et amuse-toi.</p>
        <a href="<%= search_cards_path %>" class="landing-badge">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Direction fouille intensive</button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 py-3">
        <img src="https://media.magic.wizards.com/4717DZwYAI.png" alt="Carrousel slide 3" class="d-block w-100 rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-center flex-column py-4 mb-3">
    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading col-12 col-md-5 d-flex flex-column mb-3 order-md-2">Voici un outil qui va te faire voir en grand
          <span class="text-muted">ta collection.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="lead">Ta collection est visible entièrement ici. Tu vas pouvoir voir le prix unitaire de chacune de tes cartes.</p>
        <a href="<%= cards_path %>" class="landing-badge">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Direction calculette en main!</button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 py-3 order-md-1">
        <img src="https://media.magic.wizards.com/images/featured/EN_VisitedPlanes_Alara_0.png" alt="Carrousel slide 3" class="d-block w-100 rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-center flex-column py-4 mb-3">
    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2
          class="featurette-heading col-12 col-md-5 py-4 d-flex flex-column mb-3 order-md-2">L'outil qui te permet
          <span class="text-muted">de voir loin.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="lead">Maintenant, on analyse le prix de ta collection ainsi que son évolution les mois/ans passés.<br>
          Ce prix reflète <b> une estimation</b> globale de ta collection.
        </p>
        <a
          href="<%= construction_path %>" class="landing-badge">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Direction feuille de calcul !</button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 py-3">
        <img src="https://media.magic.wizards.com/images/featured/EN_VisitedPlanes_Dominaria_0.png" alt="Carrousel slide 3" class="d-block w-100 rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-center flex-column py-4 mb-3">
    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading col-12 col-md-5 d-flex flex-column mb-3 py-4 order-md-2">Enfin, voici ce que l'aléatoire signifie réellement.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Découvre <a href="<%= random_path %>">ici</a> une carte aléatoire à chaque clique, un vrai délice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 py-3 order-md-1">
        <img src="https://media.magic.wizards.com/images/featured/EN_VisitedPlanes_Kamigawa_0.png" alt="Carrousel slide 3" class="d-block w-100 rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->

<hr class="featurette-divider py-4">

<!-- START CAROUSEL -->

<div class="container">
  <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
    <!-- Indicateurs -->
    <div class="carousel-indicators">
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-label="Slide 1" aria-current="true"></button>
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2" class=""></button>
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3" class=""></button>
    </div>
    <!-- Carrousel -->
    <div class="carousel-inner rounded">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img src="https://media.magic.wizards.com/images/background/QBjbFxpkQO.jpg" alt="Carrousel slide 1" class="d-block w-100">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
            <h2>« La vie et la mort sont toutes deux réversibles. »</h2>
            <p>—Nicol Bolas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="https://media.magic.wizards.com/images/background/LLAgGw8k8q_0.jpg" alt="Carrousel slide 2" class="d-block w-100">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h2>« Une récompense qui en vaut la peine ne s'obtient jamais facilement. »</h2>
            <p>—Nicol Bolas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="https://media.magic.wizards.com/images/background/gWFYSs5Zmh.jpg" alt="Carrousel slide 3" class="d-block w-100">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
            <h2>« Les innocents paient-ils pour les coupables ? Bien entendu. Tel est le destin des faibles. »</h2>
            <p>—Nicol Bolas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Controls -->
    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- /END CAROUSEL -->
